{"tid":134450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首爾大學校花性愛片流出 淫聲浪語轟動校園","createTime":"2017-02-25T13:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T13:21:00.000Z","uid":5600,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba2fd99e3ab631031000487adaec0e0c2c7bff2e","tid":134450,"uid":5600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T13:09:12.000Z","msg":"南韓傳媒報道，涉事的為一名首爾大學的校花，由於她外型清純、身材姣好，受到許多男同學愛慕，近日一名自稱是她前男友的人，在網上散播該校花的性愛影片，該男子更自豪留言：「跟她每一次性愛都令人難忘。」報道沒有披露該名校花的真實姓名。<br />\n<br />\n該段影片在流出後不足一天已被移除，目前網上只傳出有關影片的截圖，據媒體報道，該段影片尺度大膽，當中涉及不少高難度性愛姿勢，而且片段內淫聲浪語，與該校花平日的清純形象大相逕庭，據報道，該校花在影片曝光後，已向大學請假，沒有再返回校園，暫時消聲匿跡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2017/02/20170224_PN_%E6%A0%A1%E8%8A%B12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2017%2F02%2F20170224_PN_%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E8%258A%25B12.jpg&h=73e461b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"980f0c13beec98512d560a7e5992366dd97d51bb","tid":134450,"uid":31539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T13:09:54.000Z","msg":"又冇link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b877152c05c84cfe90073104e595f11dfbf71450","tid":134450,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T13:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c3c859cf6ae8529493d614cb590b88eba141